535
00:50:50,199 --> 00:50:52,719
[SPEAKER_01] A taj novac u toj kompaniji

536
00:50:52,719 --> 00:50:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] treba da pomogne svima da ostvare svoje targete

537
00:50:56,159 --> 00:50:57,980
[SPEAKER_01] svaku na svom nivou.

538
00:50:59,119 --> 00:51:00,780
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, čistačica na njenom nivou,

539
00:51:00,780 --> 00:51:02,360
[SPEAKER_01] magacioner na njegovom nivou,

540
00:51:02,360 --> 00:51:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] prodava sa njegovom nivou,

541
00:51:03,840 --> 00:51:04,940
[SPEAKER_01] medađer na njegovom nivou,

542
00:51:04,940 --> 00:51:06,199
[SPEAKER_01] vlastnik na njegovom nivou.

543
00:51:06,199 --> 00:51:09,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ako su svi tu negde zadovoljni,

544
00:51:09,260 --> 00:51:11,719
[SPEAKER_01] to će moći da funkcioniše i traje.

545
00:51:11,719 --> 00:51:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi će biti lojalni.

546
00:51:12,800 --> 00:51:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] U ekonomiji imaš istu situaciju.

547
00:51:15,800 --> 00:51:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako, ne znam, banke podignu kamatne stope,

548
00:51:18,920 --> 00:51:21,780
[SPEAKER_01] privreda se manje zadužuje,

549
00:51:21,780 --> 00:51:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] građani se manje zadužuju

550
00:51:23,199 --> 00:51:25,480
[SPEAKER_01] i dođe, pada potrošnije, dođe do krize.

551
00:51:26,219 --> 00:51:27,780
[SPEAKER_01] Banke spuste kamatne stope

552
00:51:27,780 --> 00:51:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] ispod neke normalne vrednosti,

553
00:51:29,599 --> 00:51:31,199
[SPEAKER_01] privreda uzima više kapitala,

554
00:51:31,199 --> 00:51:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] građani uzme više kapitala,

555
00:51:32,480 --> 00:51:33,219
[SPEAKER_01] dođe do inflacije.

556
00:51:33,219 --> 00:51:35,860
[SPEAKER_01] Kad god se izađe iz tog balansa,

557
00:51:35,860 --> 00:51:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] da je svima dobro,

558
00:51:37,059 --> 00:51:38,739
[SPEAKER_01] nastaje problem.

559
00:51:40,940 --> 00:51:45,719
[SPEAKER_00] To je malo, možda i percepcija da je svima dobro.

560
00:51:45,719 --> 00:51:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] Možda kad gledaš neki manji komad planete

561
00:51:50,980 --> 00:51:52,800
[SPEAKER_00] ili ljudi i tako dalje,

562
00:51:52,800 --> 00:51:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako uzmeš cijelu planetu,

563
00:51:53,980 --> 00:51:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] u obzir,

564
00:51:54,380 --> 00:51:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] rijetko si kad decilo da smo uravno teži.

565
00:51:57,519 --> 00:51:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde da popričamo i na tu temu.

566
00:51:59,119 --> 00:52:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde pogledaj jednu stvar.

567
00:52:00,679 --> 00:52:03,099
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ovo su moji uvidi.

568
00:52:04,360 --> 00:52:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] rađujem se od bilo tome da dajem bilo kakvu analizu.

569
00:52:07,519 --> 00:52:09,219
[SPEAKER_01] Još, još.

570
00:52:09,219 --> 00:52:13,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ajde pogledamo interesantno.

571
00:52:13,059 --> 00:52:16,039
[SPEAKER_01] Zemlje koje su postigle neki

572
00:52:16,039 --> 00:52:20,760
[SPEAKER_01] najviše stadijum kvaliteta života.

573
00:52:20,760 --> 00:52:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] Sistemski su stvari popakoli kako treba.

574
00:52:24,380 --> 00:52:28,659
[SPEAKER_01] Norveška, Švedska, Danska, Belgija, Holandija

575
00:52:28,659 --> 00:52:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

576
00:52:30,000 --> 00:52:33,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znači oni su napravili dobar sistem.

577
00:52:34,360 --> 00:52:36,139
[SPEAKER_01] Napravili su socijalne zaštite.

578
00:52:36,139 --> 00:52:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dobre penzijene fondove,

579
00:52:38,500 --> 00:52:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] investicijone je spakovali infrastrukturu gradove.

580
00:52:40,960 --> 00:52:42,179
[SPEAKER_01] Zatvorili granice.

581
00:52:42,179 --> 00:52:43,099
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dalje.

582
00:52:43,099 --> 00:52:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] I mi živimo super.

583
00:52:45,239 --> 00:52:48,760
[SPEAKER_01] Teško se ulazi, teško se dobio viza i tako dalje.

584
00:52:48,760 --> 00:52:50,860
[SPEAKER_01] Rezultat.

585
00:52:50,860 --> 00:52:53,360
[SPEAKER_01] Bela kuga.

586
00:52:53,360 --> 00:52:55,480
[SPEAKER_01] Pad nataliteta.

587
00:52:55,480 --> 00:52:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] Nema porasta.

588
00:52:57,619 --> 00:53:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] I ono što je vrlo interesantno

589
00:53:01,760 --> 00:53:05,019
[SPEAKER_01] kod mladih ljudi

590
00:53:05,019 --> 00:53:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] porast nezadovoljstva,

591
00:53:07,239 --> 00:53:08,739
[SPEAKER_01] akcijoznosti,

592
00:53:08,739 --> 00:53:10,639
[SPEAKER_01] demencije.

593
00:53:10,639 --> 00:53:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] Gore u skaniravskim državkom.

594
00:53:12,559 --> 00:53:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači jako veliki broj mladih ljudi

595
00:53:15,800 --> 00:53:17,579
[SPEAKER_01] koji imaju porast demencije.

596
00:53:17,579 --> 00:53:17,960
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

597
00:53:17,960 --> 00:53:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što smisao života je da naša duša

598
00:53:20,380 --> 00:53:21,360
[SPEAKER_01] prikuplja iskustva.

599
00:53:21,360 --> 00:53:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] Što znači mi treba da ulazimo u novo.

600
00:53:23,900 --> 00:53:25,159
[SPEAKER_01] Mi treba da istražujemo.

601
00:53:25,159 --> 00:53:26,280
[SPEAKER_01] Mi treba da gradimo.

602
00:53:26,280 --> 00:53:27,400
[SPEAKER_01] Mi treba da stvaramo.

603
00:53:27,539 --> 00:53:29,019
[SPEAKER_01] ono do ređenja ne mora ništa.

604
00:53:29,019 --> 00:53:33,780
[SPEAKER_01] Socijalna zaštita, super,

605
00:53:33,780 --> 00:53:34,760
[SPEAKER_01] sve je ekstra.

606
00:53:34,760 --> 00:53:35,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ono,

607
00:53:35,559 --> 00:53:37,219
[SPEAKER_01] neću da rađem decu.

608
00:53:37,219 --> 00:53:39,940
[SPEAKER_01] Jedno ću da putojmo,

609
00:53:39,940 --> 00:53:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] ću da uživam.

610
00:53:40,539 --> 00:53:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali i to je iskustvo isto.

611
00:53:41,920 --> 00:53:43,239
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste, ne kažem da nije.

612
00:53:43,239 --> 00:53:44,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ali šta se dešava?

613
00:53:44,179 --> 00:53:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] E onda se dešava pošto

614
00:53:45,739 --> 00:53:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] tu sad nešto fali

615
00:53:47,380 --> 00:53:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda dolaze ljudi sa strane.

616
00:53:49,000 --> 00:53:50,719
[SPEAKER_01] Dolaze upravo iz tih zemalja

617
00:53:50,719 --> 00:53:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] gde je katastrofa za život.

618
00:53:52,260 --> 00:53:53,139
[SPEAKER_01] Dolaze iz Afrike,

619
00:53:53,139 --> 00:53:54,119
[SPEAKER_01] dolaze iz Azije,

620
00:53:54,119 --> 00:53:54,760
[SPEAKER_01] dolaze ovdje.

621
00:53:54,760 --> 00:53:56,739
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, oni će da rade one postave

622
00:53:56,739 --> 00:53:57,519
[SPEAKER_01] koje mi nećemo.

623
00:53:57,519 --> 00:53:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] A hteli, ne hteli,

624
00:53:58,260 --> 00:54:00,360
[SPEAKER_01] priroda gura u ravnotežu.

625
00:54:00,360 --> 00:54:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne možeš.

626
00:54:01,019 --> 00:54:03,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, Jim si postao sebičan.

627
00:54:03,780 --> 00:54:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, misliš samo na sebe

628
00:54:05,539 --> 00:54:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] i onda ti priroda polako vraća

629
00:54:06,980 --> 00:54:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] u ravnotežu

630
00:54:07,940 --> 00:54:09,300
[SPEAKER_01] i gura ti te ljude tamo

631
00:54:09,300 --> 00:54:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] i automatski

632
00:54:10,079 --> 00:54:11,239
[SPEAKER_01] ti sad kada pogledaš

633
00:54:11,239 --> 00:54:13,260
[SPEAKER_01] realno i Francusku

634
00:54:13,260 --> 00:54:14,280
[SPEAKER_01] i Holandiju

635
00:54:14,280 --> 00:54:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

636
00:54:15,199 --> 00:54:16,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja ne znam,

637
00:54:16,340 --> 00:54:18,760
[SPEAKER_01] oni više nemaju naciju,

638
00:54:18,760 --> 00:54:19,480
[SPEAKER_01] oni imaju državu.

639
00:54:19,480 --> 00:54:20,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, pogledaš

640
00:54:20,320 --> 00:54:22,280
[SPEAKER_01] francusku reprezentaciju.

641
00:54:22,280 --> 00:54:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] Gledao sam Francuska Marokka,

642
00:54:24,840 --> 00:54:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] znači, u Maroku Belije,

643
00:54:26,179 --> 00:54:27,139
[SPEAKER_01] u Francusko Svitorlje

644
00:54:27,139 --> 00:54:27,760
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

645
00:54:27,760 --> 00:54:29,280
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, priroda to vraća

646
00:54:29,280 --> 00:54:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] sve na svoje mesto.

647
00:54:30,019 --> 00:54:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kad mi razmišljamo

648
00:54:32,119 --> 00:54:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] da svima bude dobro,

649
00:54:33,380 --> 00:54:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] to je prirodno,

650
00:54:34,699 --> 00:54:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] to je u skladu sa ljubavlju.

651
00:54:35,800 --> 00:54:37,920
[SPEAKER_01] Čim razmišljamo sebičan,

652
00:54:37,920 --> 00:54:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] samo meni da bude dobro,

653
00:54:39,079 --> 00:54:40,159
[SPEAKER_01] onda se priroda umeša.

654
00:54:40,159 --> 00:54:42,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nam to ubaci neke parametre

655
00:54:42,179 --> 00:54:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] da vraća stvari na svoje mesto.

656
00:54:43,260 --> 00:54:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da, mislim, možeš,

657
00:54:43,739 --> 00:54:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] htio sam ti komentirati

658
00:54:45,099 --> 00:54:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] ljubav koju si spomenio

659
00:54:46,699 --> 00:54:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] prije desetak minuta.

660
00:54:47,860 --> 00:54:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

661
00:54:48,340 --> 00:54:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je to isklizak teren,

662
00:54:52,980 --> 00:54:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] isto, ovo,

663
00:54:53,500 --> 00:54:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] traž.

664
00:54:54,119 --> 00:54:56,860
[SPEAKER_00] I čak kroz ovo,

665
00:54:56,860 --> 00:54:58,059
[SPEAKER_00] to je jako lijepo u definiciji

666
00:54:58,059 --> 00:54:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] da ljubav je unutrašnja snaga.

667
00:54:59,880 --> 00:55:03,719
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ti možeš,

668
00:55:03,719 --> 00:55:06,360
[SPEAKER_00] na jednom ružnom povijestnom primjeru,

669
00:55:06,360 --> 00:55:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] možeš reći da su obje strane

670
00:55:07,880 --> 00:55:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] radile,

671
00:55:08,920 --> 00:55:10,780
[SPEAKER_00] što su radili iz ljubavi.

672
00:55:10,780 --> 00:55:11,639
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

673
00:55:11,639 --> 00:55:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] Hitler je radio sa svojom jemačkom,

674
00:55:15,119 --> 00:55:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] što god,

675
00:55:16,139 --> 00:55:18,219
[SPEAKER_00] iz ljubavi je radio

676
00:55:18,219 --> 00:55:19,940
[SPEAKER_00] to što je radio,

677
00:55:19,940 --> 00:55:21,260
[SPEAKER_00] a isto tako s druge strane,

678
00:55:21,260 --> 00:55:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] savjeznici su iz ljubavi

679
00:55:22,599 --> 00:55:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] se branili,

680
00:55:25,239 --> 00:55:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali u tom činu

681
00:55:28,099 --> 00:55:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] ljubavi s obje strane

682
00:55:29,059 --> 00:55:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] smo stvorili strašno puno

683
00:55:30,639 --> 00:55:31,679
[SPEAKER_00] konflikta, nasilja,

684
00:55:31,679 --> 00:55:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] ubojstava i tako dalje.

685
00:55:33,900 --> 00:55:34,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može se iz ljubavi

686
00:55:34,559 --> 00:55:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] raditi na šta je to drugog.

687
00:55:36,000 --> 00:55:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

688
00:55:38,920 --> 00:55:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] pitanje je kako tko

689
00:55:40,500 --> 00:55:41,280
[SPEAKER_00] razumije ljubav.

690
00:55:41,280 --> 00:55:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] Saj, okej,

691
00:55:41,659 --> 00:55:42,880
[SPEAKER_01] kako tko tumače ljubav.

692
00:55:42,880 --> 00:55:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] To sam apsolutno,

693
00:55:43,800 --> 00:55:44,699
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ja ne ulazim

694
00:55:44,699 --> 00:55:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] u apsolutno tumačenje ljubavi

695
00:55:46,619 --> 00:55:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] da svi treba

696
00:55:47,480 --> 00:55:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] da prihvate definiciju.

697
00:55:48,960 --> 00:55:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] Netko je zato što je išao

698
00:55:49,920 --> 00:55:51,159
[SPEAKER_00] zaštiti svoju obitelj

699
00:55:51,159 --> 00:55:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] ili zato što mu je netko,

700
00:55:52,340 --> 00:55:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] znaš,

701
00:55:54,579 --> 00:55:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] najbolje u našoj zapadnoj kulturi

702
00:55:57,460 --> 00:55:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] i po mom iskustvu

703
00:55:58,519 --> 00:55:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] i po mom mišljenju

704
00:55:59,500 --> 00:56:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] tko je najbolje opisao ljubavi

705
00:56:00,920 --> 00:56:01,639
[SPEAKER_00] je Isus.

706
00:56:01,639 --> 00:56:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

707
00:56:03,559 --> 00:56:04,739
[SPEAKER_00] tko je danas premano

708
00:56:04,739 --> 00:56:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] krenuti drugi obraz

709
00:56:05,739 --> 00:56:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] kad ti neko nešto nabroji,

710
00:56:07,940 --> 00:56:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] nažadno.

711
00:56:08,420 --> 00:56:09,320
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

712
00:56:10,320 --> 00:56:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

713
00:56:10,960 --> 00:56:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] tebi netko pored tebe

714
00:56:12,539 --> 00:56:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] pokazuje mišiće,

715
00:56:13,840 --> 00:56:14,639
[SPEAKER_00] sad ti trebaš

716
00:56:14,639 --> 00:56:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] se, ono,

717
00:56:16,500 --> 00:56:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] smilovat,

718
00:56:17,159 --> 00:56:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] biti ponizan

719
00:56:17,980 --> 00:56:19,219
[SPEAKER_00] i okrenuti drugi obraz

720
00:56:19,219 --> 00:56:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] da je,

721
00:56:19,420 --> 00:56:21,760
[SPEAKER_00] udari me po drugom obrazu.

722
00:56:21,760 --> 00:56:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] I sad,

723
00:56:22,440 --> 00:56:24,320
[SPEAKER_00] ljubav je nekada

724
00:56:24,320 --> 00:56:26,559
[SPEAKER_01] i pokazati otpor.

725
00:56:26,559 --> 00:56:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je ljubav prema sebi.

726
00:56:29,340 --> 00:56:30,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kompleksno je,

727
00:56:30,340 --> 00:56:31,179
[SPEAKER_01] slojevito je.

728
00:56:31,179 --> 00:56:32,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ako sam napadnuti,

729
00:56:32,860 --> 00:56:33,579
[SPEAKER_01] ugrožen,

730
00:56:33,579 --> 00:56:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] životno bezbeden,

731
00:56:34,699 --> 00:56:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] ja iz ljubavi prema sebi

732
00:56:35,800 --> 00:56:36,679
[SPEAKER_01] se moram braniti.

733
00:56:36,679 --> 00:56:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dalje.

734
00:56:40,099 --> 00:56:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] da ne ulazimo

735
00:56:41,380 --> 00:56:42,780
[SPEAKER_01] u te kontekste.

736
00:56:42,780 --> 00:56:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ali

737
00:56:43,679 --> 00:56:45,320
[SPEAKER_01] unutrašnja snaga

738
00:56:45,320 --> 00:56:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] da uradim

739
00:56:47,019 --> 00:56:48,860
[SPEAKER_01] za dobrobit sebe

740
00:56:48,860 --> 00:56:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] i drugih paralelno.

741
00:56:50,500 --> 00:56:52,280
[SPEAKER_01] Realno govoreći,

742
00:56:52,280 --> 00:56:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne mogu da pravim razliku

743
00:56:53,780 --> 00:56:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] među mene i tebe.

744
00:56:54,659 --> 00:56:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

745
00:56:55,539 --> 00:56:56,800
